*2018年： {{tsl|en|Nature-based solutions|基于自然的解决方案}}（口号：大自然在呼唤）<ref>{{cite web |title=World Water Development Report 2018 |url=http://www.unwater.org/publications/world-water-development-report-2018/ |website=UN-Water |location=Geneva, Switzerland |accessdate=2020-08-25 |date=2018-03-19 |archive-date=2019-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190908083130/http://www.unwater.org/publications/world-water-development-report-2018/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* 2017年： [[廢水|廢水]]<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.unwater.org/publications/world-water-development-report-2017/|title=World Water Development Report 2017|website=UN-Water|language=en-US|access-date=2018-11-12|archive-date=2018-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181108031041/http://www.unwater.org/publications/world-water-development-report-2017/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
